  "label": "Sevrik Ashmere",
  "description": "This individual is an undead of medium stature, preserved in a glass-sheened ruin of flesh consistent with the Vitrified Rift’s heat-scorched catastrophe. Black hair lies in brittle, fused strands along the scalp, and gray eyes sit sunken beneath a brow creased into permanent strain. Bronze skin bears wide plates of vitrification across the cheek and collar, interrupting the living grain with opaque, cracked glaze. The mouth’s fixed asymmetry and the stiff set of the neck give the figure a judicial, accusatory cast even in stillness.",
