    "personality": "Methodical and mute, this undead maintains a relentless patrol of the Rift’s glassed corridors, halting to study intruders with a prosecutorial attention shaped by old tribunal routines. It responds to bright flame and loud prayer with immediate aggression, but ignores ordinary speech, treating the living as fugitives rather than prey. Its conduct follows fixed circuits and repeated gestures, as if bound to a remembered docket and the unfinished accounting of the dead.",
